<section class="bg-white py-24 overflow-hidden border-b border-slate-200"> <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"> <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center mb-16 reveal-up"> <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">Kasus Penggunaan</span> <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">Satu AI Agent, Beragam Solusi Bisnis.</h2> <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600"> AI Agent kami sangat fleksibel dan dapat dilatih menjadi ahli di industri apa pun. Berikut adalah beberapa skenario bagaimana AI kami mengotomatisasi bisnis klien. </p> </div> <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center"> <!-- Text Content --> <div class="space-y-8 reveal-left"> <!-- Use Case 1 --> <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-300"> <div class="flex items-start gap-4"> <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-orange-100 text-orange-600"> <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z"></path></svg> </div> <div> <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">E-Commerce & Retail</h3> <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"> Menjawab pertanyaan stok produk real-time, merekomendasikan ukuran/warna yang cocok, membantu proses checkout, dan menginformasikan status resi pengiriman otomatis. </p> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Use Case 2 --> <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-300"> <div class="flex items-start gap-4"> <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600"> <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg> </div> <div> <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">Klinik & Jasa Profesional</h3> <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"> Booking jadwal dokter atau layanan 24 jam sehari. AI akan mengecek ketersediaan kalender, mendaftarkan nama pasien, dan mengirimkan reminder H-1 via WhatsApp. </p> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Use Case 3 --> <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md hover:border-blue-300"> <div class="flex items-start gap-4"> <div class="flex h-12 w-12 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-purple-100 text-purple-600"> <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg> </div> <div> <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">B2B & Properti (Lead Gen)</h3> <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"> Menyaring *cold leads* menjadi *hot leads* di tengah malam. AI menanyakan budget, kebutuhan proyek/properti, dan otomatis memasukkan data ke CRM (HubSpot/Salesforce) untuk difollow-up tim Sales besok paginya. </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- Image Area for Bos to Replace (Right side on Desktop) --> <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-lg lg:max-w-none reveal-right delay-200"> <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-l from-emerald-100 to-blue-100 blur-2xl opacity-50 rounded-[3rem]"></div> <div class="relative rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-100 border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden shadow-xl aspect-[4/3] flex items-center justify-center group"> <img src="/assets/images/use-cases.png" alt="Ilustrasi Use Cases AI Agent" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-10 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" /> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section>
